name: AlbanianIdNumberTest
description: Test suite for validating and generating Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: valid
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of a valid Albanian ID number and checks its length.

test_cases.name: invalid
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an invalid Albanian ID number, checks its length, and validates a specific part of the number.

test_cases.name: yy
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of year to a specific format used in Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: mm
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of month based on gender for Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: dd
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of day to a specific format used in Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: checksum
test_cases.description: Tests the checksum calculation for Albanian ID numbers.

test_cases.name: checksumOfFirstChar
test_cases.description: Tests the checksum calculation of the first character for Albanian ID numbers.
